data.description: Open concept house that would be perfect for a duck lodge or family. This house has a large living room that flows into the dining area and then into the kitchen. The kitchen also has a bar area for extra seating. Right off the kitchen you will find a large mud room/laundry room to store all your hunting gear. This home features two large bedrooms and one large bath. Outside you will find ample parking and a workshop for extra storage.  All information is believed to be accurate, but is not warranted in any way.
